---
// About section — bio, meta info, and four strength cards
---

<section class="block" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="label">
      <span class="bar"></span>
      <span class="num">01</span>
      <span>ABOUT</span>
    </div>
    
    <h2 class="display">A BUILDER<br />WITH <span class="accent">A SECOND ACT.</span></h2>
    
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-meta">
        <dl>
          <dt>Based in</dt>
          <dd>Vancouver, BC</dd>
          <dt>Studying</dt>
          <dd>Computer Science, UBC</dd>
          <dt>Graduating</dt>
          <dd>May 2027 (Expected)</dd>
          <dt>Open to</dt>
          <dd>SWE Internships, Fall and Winter 2026-2027</dd>
        </dl>
      </div>
      <div>
  <blockquote class="blockquote">
    I loved journalism because I loved seeing people connect — when we understand each other better, even <em>the parts we dislike start to make sense.</em>
  </blockquote>
  <p class="about-body">
    Currently a final-year CS student at the University of British Columbia, focused on backend systems, APIs, and developer tooling. I'm drawn to projects where engineering meets a real human workflow — voice handoffs for nonprofits, calendar plumbing for university testing facilities, schema design that holds up at 3NF.
  </p>
  <p class="about-body">
    Before UBC, I worked in Korean broadcasting and digital news. I'm starting to think tech can do what journalism did for me — bring people closer to systems they don't fully understand. That's the kind of work I want to keep finding.
  </p>
  <p class="about-body">
    That background still shows up in how I build: I care about the people on the other side of the screen — what they need, what frustrates them, what they don't say out loud.
  </p>

</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="strength-grid">
      <div class="strength">
        <span class="idx">/01</span>
        <h4>Backend &amp; APIs</h4>
        <p>FastAPI, Node.js, and Oracle. Designing endpoints with draft/confirm separation, OAuth flows, and full referential integrity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="strength">
        <span class="idx">/02</span>
        <h4>AI Integration</h4>
        <p>OpenAI Whisper across 50+ languages and GPT-4o-mini for structured JSON extraction — turning 5-minute voice handoffs into 30-second records.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="strength">
        <span class="idx">/03</span>
        <h4>Shipping &amp; Iteration</h4>
        <p>Co-shipped a Chrome Extension serving 29 active users, currently coordinating with a UBC facility director for an official endorsement.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="strength">
        <span class="idx">/04</span>
        <h4>Editorial Eye</h4>
        <p>Eight years in newsrooms and live broadcast control rooms. I prioritize ruthlessly, write tight, and don't break under deadline pressure.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .block {
    padding: 160px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-muted);
    position: relative;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .block { padding: 100px 0; }
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1440px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 64px;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .container { padding: 0 24px; }
  }

  .label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .label .num {
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .label .bar {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 48px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .display {
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(56px, 9vw, 100px);
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: var(--color-global-text);
  }

  .display .accent {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 5fr 7fr;
    gap: 80px;
    margin-top: 64px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
  }

  .about-meta dt {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .about-meta dd {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-global-text);
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .about-meta dt:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .blockquote {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding: 8px 0 8px 24px;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--color-global-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .blockquote em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about-body {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-top: 28px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .about-body + .about-body {
    margin-top: 18px;
  }

.strength-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1px;
  margin-top: 80px;
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-global-text) 12%, transparent);
  border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-global-text) 12%, transparent);
}
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .strength-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

 .strength {
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-global-text) 6%, var(--color-global-bg));
  padding: 36px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 14px;
  min-height: 200px;
  transition: background 0.25s ease;
}

.strength:hover {
  background: var(--color-global-bg);
}

  .strength .idx {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .strength h4 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--color-global-text);
  }

  .strength p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }
</style>